Note: Runa GCP (Google Cloud Platform) Integration Module
Note: Provides comprehensive Google Cloud Platform services management functionality
Note: Following Runa specification patterns with natural language syntax

Note: Built-in functions are automatically available in Runa programs
Note: No imports required for built-ins like create_runtime_error, execute_command, etc.

Note: GCP Compute Engine Instance type definition
Type called "GCPInstance":
    instance_id as String,
    name as String,
    zone as String,
    machine_type as String,
    status as String,
    internal_ip as String,
    external_ip as Optional[String],
    network_interfaces as List[Dictionary[String, Any]],
    disks as List[Dictionary[String, Any]],
    metadata as Dictionary[String, String],
    labels as Dictionary[String, String],
    service_accounts as List[Dictionary[String, Any]],
    creation_timestamp as Integer,
    last_start_timestamp as Optional[Integer],
    can_ip_forward as Boolean,
    scheduling as Dictionary[String, Any]

Note: GCP Cloud Storage Bucket type definition
Type called "GCPBucket":
    name as String,
    location as String,
    location_type as String,
    storage_class as String,
    versioning_enabled as Boolean,
    lifecycle_configuration as Optional[List[Dictionary[String, Any]]],
    cors_configuration as Optional[List[Dictionary[String, Any]]],
    website_configuration as Optional[Dictionary[String, Any]],
    encryption as Dictionary[String, Any],
    iam_configuration as Dictionary[String, Any],
    retention_policy as Optional[Dictionary[String, Any]],
    creation_time as Integer,
    updated_time as Integer,
    labels as Dictionary[String, String]

Note: GCP Cloud Storage Object type definition
Type called "GCPObject":
    name as String,
    bucket as String,
    generation as String,
    metageneration as String,
    content_type as String,
    size as Integer,
    md5_hash as String,
    crc32c as String,
    etag as String,
    creation_time as Integer,
    updated_time as Integer,
    storage_class as String,
    metadata as Dictionary[String, String],
    cache_control as Optional[String],
    content_disposition as Optional[String],
    content_encoding as Optional[String],
    content_language as Optional[String]

